OL,6,FA married couple died of gunshot
OL,7,Fwounds to the head in their Trowbridge
OL,8,Fhome, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FThe bodies of Christine Jefferies, 72,
OL,11,Fand her 74-year-old husband Stephen
OL,12,Fwere discovered at a house in Morfa
OL,13,FCrescent in the Trowbridge area of
OL,14,FCardiff on the afternoon of 5 October.
OL,16,FSouth Wales Police said they also
OL,17,Frecovered the body of a dog and a
OL,18,Frifle.
