OL,6,FThe inquest opened into their deaths
OL,7,Fat South Wales Coroner's Court in
OL,8,FPontypridd on Wednesday.
OL,10,FThe hearing heard how the bodies of Mr
OL,11,Fand Mrs Jefferies were discovered by
OL,12,Ftheir daughter who let herself into
OL,13,Fthe house after there had been no
OL,14,Freply at the door.
OL,16,FPost-mortems recorded their
OL,17,Fprovisional causes of death as both
OL,18,Fhaving a gunshot wound to the temple.
